sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K801003
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: pTUM103 yeast shuttle vector with pADH1 promoter
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Georg Sch??tzinger
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part corresponds to pTUM100 (BBa_K801000). The constitutive pADH1 promoter has been cloned in front of the MCS (RFC25 prefix and suffix).
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: All forbidden restriction sites have been removed from the plasmid backbone, making it RFC25 compatible .
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Based on invitrogen's pYES2 plasmid. For more information see the part information of pTUM100 (BBa_K801000).
